unittitle_ssm: Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Collection of AFL-CIO Serials
abstract_ssm: The Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Collection of AFL-CIO Serials contains over 100 titles published by and about the American Federation of Labor and Congress of Industrial Organizations.  The collection dates between 1887 and 2001, with the bulk of the material dating from the 1940s through the 1980s.  Topics include labor related convention proceedings, council and president reports, and United States politics.
